text: Oscar or Óscar Gómez may refer to: * Óscar Rendoll Gómez (born 1916), Chilean football manager * Óscar Gómez Sánchez (born 1934), Peruvian footballer * Oscar R. Gómez (born 1956), Argentine writer, psychoanalyst and academic researcher * Óscar Gómez Barbero (born 1961), corporate director of Information Systems at RENFE, the Spanish state railways * Oscar Gómez (boxer) (born 1975), Argentine boxer * Óscar Freire Gómez (born 1976), a former Spanish road bicycle racer
title: Oscar Gómez
